<div id="main-article" class="article-content retro-folders">
<p>A series of <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/Omnibus" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/Omnibus">Omnibus</a> books by <a class="createlink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/SidgwickAndJackson" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/SidgwickAndJackson">Sidgwick &amp; Jackson</a>. It includes <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/Novel" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/Novel">Novels</a> and <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/Anthology" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/Anthology">Anthologies</a>, often forming <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/Doorstopper" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/Doorstopper">Doorstopper-length</a> hardcover books. Forty-four different books were published in this series, all in hardback.</p><hr><h2>Works published in the <em>Science Fiction Special</em> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/Omnibus" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/Omnibus">Omnibus</a> series:</h2><div class="folderlabel" onclick="toggleAllFolders();">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;open/close all folders&nbsp; </div><div class="proper-ad-unit mobile-ad square_ad"><h6 class="ad-caption">Advertisement:</h6><div id="proper-ad-tvtropes_mobile_ad_1"><script>propertag.cmd.push(function() { proper_display('tvtropes_mobile_ad_1'); })</script></div></div><p></p><div class="folderlabel" onclick="togglefolder('folder0');">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Science Fiction Special 1 (1970)&nbsp;</div><div id="folder0" class="folder" isfolder="true" style="display:block;"><ul><li> <em><a class="createlink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/TheWorldJonesMade" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/TheWorldJonesMade">The World Jones Made</a></em>, by <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/PhilipKDick" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/PhilipKDick">Philip K. Dick</a> (1956)</li><li> <em><a class="createlink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/TheSpaceSwimmers" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/TheSpaceSwimmers">The Space Swimmers</a></em>, by <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/GordonRDickson" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/GordonRDickson">Gordon R. Dickson</a> (1967)</li><li> <em><a class="createlink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/WatersOfDeath" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/WatersOfDeath">Waters Of Death</a></em>, by <a class="createlink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/IrvingAGreenfield" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/IrvingAGreenfield">Irving A Greenfield</a> (1967)</li></ul></div><p></p><div class="folderlabel" onclick="togglefolder('folder1');">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Science Fiction Special 2 (1970)&nbsp;</div><div id="folder1" class="folder" isfolder="true" style="display:block;"><ul><li> <em><a class="createlink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/TheListeners" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/TheListeners">The Listeners</a></em>, by <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/MurrayLeinster" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/MurrayLeinster">Murray Leinster</a> (1969)</li><li> <em><a class="createlink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/BrightNewUniverse" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/BrightNewUniverse">Bright New Universe</a></em>, by <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/JackWilliamson" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/JackWilliamson">Jack Williamson</a> (1967)</li><li> <em><a class="createlink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/EscapeIntoSpace" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/EscapeIntoSpace">Escape Into Space</a></em>, by <a class="createlink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/ECTubb" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/ECTubb">EC Tubb</a> (1969)</li></ul></div><p></p><div class="folderlabel" onclick="togglefolder('folder2');">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Science Fiction Special 3 (1971)&nbsp;</div><div id="folder2" class="folder" isfolder="true" style="display:block;"><ul><li> <em><a class="createlink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/TheTimeHoppers" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/TheTimeHoppers">The Time Hoppers</a></em>, by <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/RobertSilverberg" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/RobertSilverberg">Robert Silverberg</a> (1967)</li><li> <em><a class="createlink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/Overmind" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/Overmind">Overmind</a></em>, by <a class="createlink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/PhyllisWadsworth" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/PhyllisWadsworth">Phyllis Wadsworth</a> (1967)</li><li> <em><a class="createlink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/Caviar" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/Caviar">Caviar</a></em>, a <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/Anthology" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/Anthology">collection of works</a> by <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/TheodoreSturgeon" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/TheodoreSturgeon">Theodore Sturgeon</a> (1955)</li></ul></div><p></p><div class="folderlabel" onclick="togglefolder('folder3');">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Science Fiction Special 4 (1971)&nbsp;</div><div id="folder3" class="folder" isfolder="true" style="display:block;"><ul><li> <em><a class="createlink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/TheManInTheMaze" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/TheManInTheMaze">The Man In The Maze</a></em>, by <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/RobertSilverberg" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/RobertSilverberg">Robert Silverberg</a> (1969)</li><li> <em><a class="createlink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/TheWingedMan" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/TheWingedMan">The Winged Man</a></em>, by <a class="createlink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/EMayneHull" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/EMayneHull">E Mayne Hull</a> and <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/AEVanVogt" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/AEVanVogt">A. E. van Vogt</a> (1966)</li><li> <em><a class="createlink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/TheRose" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/TheRose">The Rose</a></em>, a <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/Anthology" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/Anthology">collection of works</a> by <a class="createlink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/CharlesLHarness" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/CharlesLHarness">Charles L Harness</a> (1966)</li></ul></div><p></p><div class="folderlabel" onclick="togglefolder('folder4');">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Science Fiction Special 5 (1971)&nbsp;</div><div id="folder4" class="folder" isfolder="true" style="display:block;"><ul><li> <em><a class="createlink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/RiteOfPassage" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/RiteOfPassage">Rite Of Passage</a></em>, by <a class="createlink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/AlexeiPansion" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/AlexeiPansion">Alexei Pansion</a> (1968)</li><li> <em><a class="createlink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/CradleOfTheSun" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/CradleOfTheSun">Cradle Of The Sun</a></em>, by <a class="createlink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/BrianStableford" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/BrianStableford">Brian Stableford</a> (1969)</li><li> <em><a class="createlink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/TheFutureMakers" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/TheFutureMakers">The Future Makers</a></em>, a <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/GenreAnthology" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/GenreAnthology">Genre Anthology</a> edited by <a class="createlink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/PeterHaining" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/PeterHaining">Peter Haining</a> (1968)</li></ul></div><div class="proper-ad-unit mobile-ad square_ad"><h6 class="ad-caption">Advertisement:</h6><div id="proper-ad-tvtropes_mobile_ad_2"><script>propertag.cmd.push(function() { proper_display('tvtropes_mobile_ad_2'); })</script></div></div><p></p><div class="folderlabel" onclick="togglefolder('folder5');">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Scien